;;; Commentary:

;; Display the image from bonjourmadame.fr
;; Updated every day at 10AM (on Europe/Paris timezone)
;;
;; Keys:
;;
;; - n: get the next image
;; - p: get the previous image
;; - h: hide the buffer (switch to the previous one)
;; - q: quit (kill the buffer)

